Division, Department, and Team updates

We believe it is important to share regular updates at various levels of the Security Division, and we use Slack as the primary mechanism for providing these updates. Our updates are open to all GitLab team members using the following process:

Start of each month: A thread per-department is started in #security_discuss by each department leader (CorpSec, ProdSec, SecAssurance, SecOps). These threads are pinned for the duration of the month. Thread template: <MONTH> <DEPARMENT> Weekly Updates Example: August Product Security Weekly Updates

